Make sure gcc and gcc-g++ are installed on your architecture.
Install the appropriate mysql-connector-c++ for your architecture. 
boost and boost-devel are also required for this.
Clone https://github.com/opcm/pcm.git
Add the directory for pcm to your path and set this value in the appropriate build file.
libnetfilter_queue and libnetfilter_queue-devel are also needed for libipq.
